    out property <string> globe: "M 12 3 A 9 9 0 1 0 12.01 3 M 3 12 L 21 12 M 12 3 C 14.5 5.4 16 8.6 16 12 C 16 15.4 14.5 18.6 12 21 C 9.5 18.6 8 15.4 8 12 C 8 8.6 9.5 5.4 12 3";
    out property <string> sliders: "M 4 8 L 20 8 M 4 16 L 20 16 M 13 8 A 2.3 2.3 0 1 0 17.01 8 M 7 16 A 2.3 2.3 0 1 0 11.01 16";
